PrecisRegulations Amending the HUMANITARIAN DESIGNATED CLASSES REGULATIONS by delaying, until December 31, 2002, the date on which they expire, and by adding Sierra Leone to the "Source Country Class" list of countries and removing Bosnia-Herzegovina and Croatia therefrom, effective June 29, 2001.

precis:
Regulations Amending the HUMANITARIAN DESIGNATED CLASSES REGULATIONS by
delaying, until December 31, 2002, the date on which they expire, and by
adding Sierra Leone to the "Source Country Class" list of countries and
removing Bosnia-Herzegovina and Croatia therefrom, effective June 29, 2001.
